type: book
title: "CRISPR Systems and Artificial Intelligence: Technical Frontiers, Therapeutic Applications, and Sociotechnical Governance"
authors:
  - family-names: Moreno
    given-names: Miguel
    orcid: "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-0746-9587"
    affiliation: "Universidad de Granada"
